1.16.1

  * Screenshot: fix showing busy cursor when saving area
    screenshot
  * Screenshot: don't translate timestamp in the filename
  * Several build fixes for possible breakages

1.16.0

  * Add --version command line option to gde2-screenshot
  * GTK+3: fix gde2-dictionary segfault with 3.21
  * GTK+3: fix lots of deprecations in all apps
  * Translations update

1.14.1

  * Require proper GTK+ version in gde2-dict.pc file
  * Some assorted fixes
  * Translations update
  * Make distcheck use currently selected GTK+ version

1.14.0

  * Drop Gde2Conf migration scripts
  * Disable effects and delay options in gde2-screenshot UI
    when launched with -ai command line argument
  * Use hyphens instead of colons in screenshot filenames
    by default
  * GTK+3: fix a lot of deprecations and some UI issues
  * Don't use -Werror flag in build
  * Some more fixes and cleanups
  * Translations update
  * Fix Changelog generation

1.12.0

  * Add application icon to gde2-system-log
  * Add timestamp instead of window name to screenshot
    filenames by default
  * Have dictionary applet background automatically painted
  * Translation fixes for gsettings schemas
  * Some more fixes and cleanups (including source tree
    reorganization)

1.10.3

  * Fixed silent rules option by dropping obsolete "shave"
    stuff
  * Made gde2-system-log remember the active log on exit
  * Fixed potential crash in gde2-system-log
  * Various other bugfixes in gde2-system-log
  * Removed dead spanish server entry from gde2-dictionary
  * Fixed gde2-dictionary's command-line options and manpage
  * Made Ctrl+A and Ctrl+C work in gde2-dictionary's search
    field

1.10.2

  * Several help fixes

1.10.1

  * Fix gschema translations

1.10.0

  * Add GTK3 support

1.8.0

  * Use yelp-tools instead of gde2-doc-utils
  * Bugfixes
